data.description: Charming bungalow living in Ellenwood. This two bedroom, one bathroom single level home has so much opportunity. Den/home office could be converted into third bedroom and a second bathroom could also be easily added. The tile in the bath has been replaced as well as refinishing of original hardwood flooring. New A/C unit and more! Large lot on .3 acres that could be fenced in for a very private back yard. Easily accessible to both I-285 as well as I- 20, you are just a half an hour to downtown Atlanta. Investors! This could be a wonderful opportunity!
